,"tag-menstruation-al-hayd","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-ramadan","tag-women-al-nisa"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9Du","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":27596,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/15\/menses-missed-sawm-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":37044,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Menses: Women make up missed fasts, not prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adhah reported: I asked Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, \u201cWhy do menstruating women make up missed fasts but not missed prayers?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cWhen we were afflicted with menstruation, we were ordered to make up missed fasts but not missed prayers.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 335 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5468,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/21\/ramadan-make-up-missed-sawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":37044,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Making up missed fasts throughout the year","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Salamah reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, said, \u201cI had to make up some fasts I missed during the month of Ramadan, but I was unable to do so until the month of Sha\u2019ban as\u00a0I was busy with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13709,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/24\/menses-not-in-your-hand\/","url_meta":{"origin":37044,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Menstruation: Your menses are not in your hand","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to me, \u201cBring me a mat from the mosque.\u201d I said, \u201cI am menstruating.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYour menses are not in your hand.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 298 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5047,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/12\/men-women-salat-al-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":37044,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Eid: Women join men for Eid prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm 'Atiyyah reported: We were ordered to come out on the day of Eid, even the young girls and menstruating women from their houses. We would stand behind the men and declare the greatness of Allah along with them, and supplicate to Allah along with them, hoping for the blessings\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3791,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/24\/muslim-who-fasts-distant-hellfire\/","url_meta":{"origin":37044,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: A Muslim who fasts will be distant from Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\"Whoever fasts a day in the way of Allah, Allah will move his face away from the Hellfire by a distance of seventy years.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2840, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1153 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41203,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/20\/salah-make-up-asr\/","url_meta":{"origin":37044,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Performing make-up prayers after \u2018Asr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: By the One who took the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, he never left praying two missed cycles after the afternoon prayer until he met Allah Almighty, even when prayer became difficult for him. He used to perform many of his prayers while sitting down. The\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.